<div class="ugc-mod reading-notes">
  <div class="hd">
    <h2>
      读书笔记&nbsp;&nbsp;· · · · · ·&nbsp;
          <span class="pl">(<a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1665921/annotation">共<span property="v:count">14</span>篇</a>)</span>

    </h2>

      <a class="redbutt rr j a_show_login" href="https://www.douban.com/register?reason=annotate" rel="nofollow"><span>我来写笔记</span></a>
  </div>
  

    <div class="bd">
      <ul class="inline-tabs">
        <li class="on"><a href="#rank" id="by_rank" >按有用程度</a></li>
        <li><a href="#page" id="by_page" >按页码先后</a></li>
        <li><a href="#time" id="by_time" >最新笔记</a></li>
      </ul>
      
  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="22939478">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sunqitom/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1136353-138.jpg" alt="文在兹" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/22939478/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/22939478/" class="">第27页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sunqitom/" class=" " title="文在兹">文在兹</a>
                (怪圈中人)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="22939478">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/22939478/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p22939478-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class=""> 

按，“不辨有此言”，“辨”字当作“办（辦）”。虽然，“辨”字为“辦”俗体，古代不区分（参说文段注）。但到魏晋时期，办、辨区别很明显。“不办”更是常见的俗语，意为“不能够”。如：

吾故知玄德不办有此，必为人所教也。（三国志）
我在彼三载，去官之日，不办有路粮。（宋书）
主人设食，原平自以家贫，父母不办有肴味，唯餐盐饭而已。（南齐书）

以上是正史里“不办有”的例子。而“不辨”意为“不能区别”..</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/22939478/">(<span class="">3回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-12-04 19:26</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">5人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p22939478-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>按，“不辨有此言”，“辨”字当作“办（辦）”。虽然，“辨”字为“辦”俗体，古代不区分（参说文段注）。但到魏晋时期，办、辨区别很明显。“不办”更是常见的俗语，意为“不能够”。如：
<blockquote><q>
吾故知玄德不办有此，必为人所教也。（三国志）
我在彼三载，去官之日，不办有路粮。（宋书）
主人设食，原平自以家贫，父母不办有肴味，唯餐盐饭而已。（南齐书）</q></blockquote><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>以上是正史里“不办有”的例子。而“不辨”意为“不能区别”，而且几乎没有“不辨有”的例子。正史里只有一处：<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div><blockquote><q>但康乐放荡，作体不辨有首尾。（南齐书。南史同）</q></blockquote><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>这里的“不辨有”其实就是“不办有”，意思是谢灵运作文章半半拉拉，不能够写完整。因为六朝时“不办”是很突出的俗语，所以这里应该还是改成“不办”更好理解。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>张湛是东晋人，这里的“不辨”也当作“不办”，意思是晏子学遵儒墨，对身体性命非常看重，不能够说出“以死为归”这样的话。

                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/22939478/#comments">3回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2012-12-04 19:26
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="22940377">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sunqitom/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1136353-138.jpg" alt="文在兹" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/22940377/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/22940377/" class="">第149页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sunqitom/" class=" " title="文在兹">文在兹</a>
                (怪圈中人)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="22940377">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/22940377/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p22940377-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class=""> 

按，此注所言，颇类佛说。然后汉《老子铭》称老子：

其二篇之书，称天地所以能长且久者，以不自生也。厥初生民，遗体相续， 其死生之义可知也。

按“遗体相续”其意亦同张湛所言“代谢相因”。疑道家本有此说，以人身为气之所化，非必袭诸佛教。
</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-12-04 20:03</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p22940377-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>按，此注所言，颇类佛说。然后汉《老子铭》称老子：
<blockquote><q>
其二篇之书，称天地所以能长且久者，以不自生也。厥初生民，遗体相续， 其死生之义可知也。</q></blockquote><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>按“遗体相续”其意亦同张湛所言“代谢相因”。疑道家本有此说，以人身为气之所化，非必袭诸佛教。

                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/22940377/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2012-12-04 20:03
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="22942282">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sunqitom/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1136353-138.jpg" alt="文在兹" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/22942282/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/22942282/" class="">第181页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sunqitom/" class=" " title="文在兹">文在兹</a>
                (怪圈中人)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="22942282">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/22942282/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p22942282-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class=""> 

可见西哲所谓“人是机器”之说，实为吾国玄学家之余唾。呵呵</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/22942282/">(<span class="">4回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-12-04 21:06</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p22942282-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>可见西哲所谓“人是机器”之说，实为吾国玄学家之余唾。呵呵
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







